// MG36PrimaryFire.
//
// Rapid fire CQC fire. Uses up ammo very quickly. 
// Very controllable, and packs a decent punch.
//
// Has accuracy and damage drop off issues due to CQC Barrel.
// Rounds detonate on target and do not penetrate.
